{% import '_templates/elements/image.twig' as Image  %}

<div class="w-full px-8 bg-white py-12 lg:py-20 hp">
    <div class="block-container">
        {% set graphBlocks = block.homepageGrid.all() %}

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            {% for block in graphBlocks[0:12] %}
                <div class="flex flex-col h-full">
                    <h5 class="font-bold h-6 overflow-hidden">{{ block.title }}</h5>
                    <div class="mb-2">{{ block.richText50 }}</div>
                    <div class="flex-grow overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
                        {% set image = block.singleImage.eagerly().one() %}
                        {{ Image.Default(image) }}
                    </div>
                </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        <div class="flex max-md:flex-wrap gap-8 pt-8">
            {% for block in graphBlocks[12:13] %}
                <div class="max-w-[700px] mx-auto">
                    <h5 class="font-bold h-6 overflow-hidden">{{ block.title }}</h5>
                    <div class="mb-2">{{ block.richText50 }}</div>
                    <div class="flex-grow overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
                        {% set image = block.singleImage.eagerly().one() %}
                        {{ Image.Default(image) }}
                    </div>
                </div>
            {% endfor %}
            <div>
                <h5 class="font-bold h-6 overflow-hidden">Composite Issues Risk Score</h5>
                <div class="mb-2">{{ block.richText50 }}</div>
                <div class="flex-grow overflow-hidden shadow-xl p-6 md:p-12 max-w-3xl">
                    <div class="flex max-md:flex-wrap max-md:justify-center max-md:gap-4 justify-between text-center pb-10">
                        <div class="w-48">
                            <h4>Risk Score</h4>
                            <h3 class="text-red-700">64.4/100</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-48">
                            <h4 class="leading-5">Change from Prior Month</h4>
                            <h3 class="text-yellow-600">â†‘ 0.7pt</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-48">
                            <h4>Risk Level</h4>
                            <h3 class="text-red-700">High</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p>
                        In addition to developments around H5N1, coverage/conversation on tariffs, layouts from regulatory bodies and immigration drove headlines for the category. Composite risk increased and the category remains the largest
                        and highest risk overall, but we've not observed shifts in sentiment, or emergence of new unfavorable narratives.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .hp img {
        object-fit: contain !important;
        background: white !important;
    }
</style>
